Package at.ac.univie.se2.ws21.team0404.app.ui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IBaseContract
    Contract interface for all MVP classes containing the base interfaces for views and presenter.
    IBaseContract.IPresenter<V extends IBaseContract.IView>
    Interface for presenter implementations to get informed about lifecycle changes.
    IBaseContract.IPresenterLifecycle<V extends IBaseContract.IView>
    Interface to inform the presenter about the view lifecycle.
    IBaseContract.IView
    Contract interface for all MVP view classes.
    IListActivityContract
    The base contract to be used by classes implementing AListActivity.
    IListActivityContract.IPresenter<T>  
    IListActivityContract.IView<T>  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ABasePresenter<V extends IBaseContract.IView>
    An abstract implementation of the presenter base interface IBaseContract.IPresenter providing basic functionality to store the ABasePresenter.view and clean up the reference on view destruction.
    AListActivity<ModelClass,​ViewHolder extends androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.ViewHolder,​Presenter extends IListActivityContract.IPresenter<ModelClass>>
    An Abstract Class used to be able to more easily create Activities, which display lists.
    AListActivityPresenter<T>
    An abstract presenter class that can be used to more simply implement presenters for the AListActivity
